  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>We're proud to say that the Chalet Hotel Alba is one of our properties run by our sister company Ski Total. Offering an authentic chalet experience in the Alps and we’re able to give you a greater choice and quality of chalets in <a data-udi="umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88}" title="Meribel">Meribel</a>.</strong></p>
<p>The property is a high quality property, set over four floors, the bedrooms all have en suite facilities and most have a balcony with picturesque mountain views.</p>
<p>With piste side location, the Chalet Hotel is only 20m from the nearest slope, allowing guests quick and easy access onto the <a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">Three Valleys Ski Area</a>. </p>
<p>The property's open plan dining and living area provides a comfortable place to unwind with friends with a glass of wine in front of the open fireplace. From the dining room, guests can look out over the sun terrace with views out across the Meribel Valleys.</p>
<p>Guests staying in the Chalet Hotel can relax at the end of a day on the slopes in the spa and wellness facilities on the lower ground floor, which features a steam room, sauna and indoor whirlpool spa bath. </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
